               <p>I saw the prosecutor lay hold of the prisoner, with the canister in his arms.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17831210-41-person496">
                  GEORGE
                   FORRESTER
               <interp inst="t17831210-41-person496" type="surname" value="FORRESTER"></interp>
